channel.title: Um Pro-dev scape..?
channel.description:
I take like 5% credit for this.
This is simply Jinrakes pvp lummy one, with removed anti leach, all saves + more stable + doesn't spam the box when someones iped ect..
I've also moved shops + added new training + added 3 new npcs that teleport you to kbd + one that teleports you to wilderness green drags + added new shop + edited items in shop.
Not much, but like i said i only take like 2% credit for this, i just moved stuff + removed anti leach.
